      <article class="post-5 page type-page status-publish has-post-thumbnail hentry" id="post-5" role="article">
       <div class="entry-content">
        <p class="lead">
         Free speech is one of UC Berkeley’s most cherished values: It is both part of our legacy as the home of the Free Speech Movement as well as central to our academic mission. This site outlines our campus’s commitment to being a place where all manner of views can be expressed — and explores some of the tensions that come alongside our fervent belief in this right.
        </p>
        <div class="sandwich pbsandwich_column">
